This folder contains a documentation archive of the JIRA Kanban board used to manage the PhantomMail GRC project.

It includes:
- A breakdown of BOA-1 through BOA-5 tasks
- Descriptions of JIRA labels used (e.g., `phantommail-poam`)
- Status updates as of July 2025
- Links between JIRA and GitHub artifacts

All items were originally created in a team-managed JIRA project using a Kanban board under the project name: **Service Stream**.
